reviewText: You need to be able to run Reg 2 discs, but this is about the only way to see these on demand.

This early Kaurismaki is not for me. I think he might be being influenced by the 1980s post-modern anti-narrative trend at the time. If you like the Man Without a Past, as I do, you may not like these because these are done in a completely different style. The descriptions of the movies sound quirky and interesting but for me, they are not.
